content.raw: This is fine. I'm being over defensive in ign-transport and I probably shouldn't print this message. This is because ign-transport has unsubscribed your service but almost at the same time you receive a request (because the other side still doesn't know about your unsubscription). The request has been discarded but I print this message. I will remove this message in a small pull request in ign-transport.
